headline: Why Haemonetics (HAE) Shares Are Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of blood products company Haemonetics (NYSE:HAE). fell 4.3% in the afternoon session after Needham downgraded the stock from 'Buy' to 'Hold', citing concerns about growing competition.

headline: Abbott Gains From Lingo CGM's Expansion on Android Platform
summary: ABT expands its Lingo biowearable to Android, broadening access to real-time glucose tracking and pushing continuous monitoring into mainstream wellness.
